quran[58]{c,v,t}:
  75,1,Ine ndilumbira pali tsiku lachiweruzo
  75,2,Ndipo ndilumbira pali munthu amene amadzidzudzula yekha
  75,3,Kodi munthu amaganiza kuti Ife sitidzalumikiza mafupa ake
  75,4,Inde Ife tikhoza kulumikiza mwaubwino nsonga za zala zake
  75,5,"Ngakhale tero, munthu amafuna kupitiliza kuchita zoipa"
  75,6,"Iye amafunsa: “Kodi zimenezi zidzachitika liti?”"
  75,7,Motero pamene maso adzathodwa
  75,8,Ndipo pamene mwezi udetsedwa
  75,9,Pamene dzuwa ndi mwezi zidzakumana
  75,10,"Patsikuli munthu adzafunsa kuti: “Kodi ndithawira kuti tsopano?”"
  75,11,Iai! Kulibe malo othawirako
  75,12,Ndi kwa Ambuye wako kokha kumene kudzakhala kothawira
  75,13,"Patsiku limeneli, munthu adzauzidwa zonse zimene adachita kuyambira poyamba mpaka pomaliza"
  75,14,Iai! Munthu adzadzichitira umboni wodzineneza yekha
  75,15,Ngakhale kuti iye azidzayesa kudzipulumutsa yekha
  75,16,Usagwedeze lilime lako zokhudza Korani ponena mofulumira
  75,17,Ndi udindo wathu kuisonkhanitsa ndi kukupatsa nzeru kuilakatula iyo
  75,18,"Ndipo pamene talakatula, tsatira mwandondomeko kalakatulidwe kake"
  75,19,Ndi udindo wathu kukufotokozera tanthauzo lake
  75,20,Iyayi!Komainumukondamoyowothamsanga
  75,21,Ndipo simufuna kulabadira za moyo umene uli nkudza
  75,22,"Nkhope zina, pa tsiku limeneli, zidzakhala zowala ndi chisangalalo"
  75,23,Zili kuyang’ana kwa Ambuye wawo
  75,24,"Ndipo nkhope zina, patsiku limeneli, zidzakhala zachisoni"
  75,25,Pozindikira kuti chilango chowawa chidzagwa pa iwo
  75,26,"Iyayi, pamene ufika mpaka pa khosi"
  75,27,"Ndipo kudzanenedwa kuti: “Kodi palibe woti angamuchize ndi kumupulumutsa ku imfa?”"
  75,28,Ndipo iye adzadziwa kuti awa ndi mathero a moyo wake
  75,29,Ndipo mwendo udzatembenuzika pa unzake
  75,30,Tsiku limeneli zonse zidzabwerera kwa Ambuye wako
  75,31,Iye sanali kuvomereza chilungamo kapena kupemphera
  75,32,Koma m’malo mwake adakana choonadi ndi kubwerera m’mbuyo
  75,33,Ndipo iye anapita kubanja lake monyada ali kudziyamikila yekha
  75,34,Tsoka kwa iwe. Ndiponso tsoka kwa iwe
  75,35,"Kachiwiri tsoka lili pafupi ndi iwe, tsopano tsoka lili pafupi"
  75,36,Kodi munthu amaganiza kuti tidzangomulekerera kuti azichita chilichonse chimene afuna
  75,37,Kodi iye sanali dontho la umuna limene lidatuluka
  75,38,Ndipo iye adakhala kam’bulu ka magazi. Ndipo Mulungu adamuumba ndipo adamukonza m’maonekedwe okongola
  75,39,"Ndipo adamulenga m’mitundu iwiri, mwamuna ndi mkazi"
  75,40,Kodi Iye alibe mphamvu yopereka moyo kwa anthu akufa
  76,1,Kodi sipadali nthawi imene munthu sanali kanthu kena kali konse kodziwika
  76,2,Ndithudi Ife tidamulenga munthu kuchokera ku madontho a umuna umene unasakanizidwa ndi ukazi ndi cholinga chomuyesa motero Ife tidamupanga iye kukhala wakumva ndi woona
  76,3,Ndithudi Ife tamulangiza njira yabwino kaya iye akhala wothokoza kapena wosathokoza
  76,4,Ndithudi tawakonzera anthu osakhulupirira unyolo ndi magoli ndi moto wa lawilawi
  76,5,Ndithudi anthu onse angwiro adzamwa chakumwa chosakanizidwa ndi madzi ochokera pa kasupe wa ku Paradiso chotchedwa Kafur
  76,6,"Kasupe amene akapolo a Mulungu adzamwapo, amene amatumphutsa madzi ochuluka"
  76,7,Iwo amene amakwaniritsa malonjezo awo ndipo amakhala ndi mantha ndi tsiku limene zoipa zidzasefukira ponseponse
  76,8,"Ndipo amapereka chakudya chifukwa cha chikondi cha Mulungu, kwa anthu aumphawi, amasiye ndi kwa akaidi"
  76,9,Ife tili kukudyetsani chifukwa cha Mulungu basi. Ife sitifuna malipiro kapena mayamiko kuchokera kwa inu
  76,10,"Ndithudi ife tiopa tsiku loopsa ndi laululu limene lidzasanduliza nkhope kuoneka monyasa, limene lili nkudza kuchokera kwa Ambuye wathu"
  76,11,Motero Mulungu awapulumutsa iwo ku zoipa za tsiku limeneli ndi kuwapatsa nyali yokongola kuti akhale mosavutika ndi mwachisangalalo
  76,12,Ndipo mphotho yawo idzakhala munda wa Paradiso ndi zovala za silika chifukwa chopirira kwawo
  76,13,"Ali kukhala m’Paradiso, pamipando yawofowofo, iwo sadzamva kutentha kwa dzuwa kapena kuzizira kwambiri"
  76,14,Ndipo mithunzi idzakhala pafupi ndi iwo ndipo zipatso zidzalendewera mu matsanzi kuti asamavutike pothyola
  76,15,Ndipo pakati pawo padzaperekedwa zikho zozungulira za siliva ndi matambula a magalasi
  76,16,"Matambula oonetsa zinthu zomwe zili m’kati mwake, opangidwa kuchokera ku siliva. Iwo adzathiramo chakumwa molingana ndi chilakolako chawo"
  76,17,Ndipo iwo adzapatsidwa chakumwa kuchokera mu zikho zodzala ndi madzi osakaniza ndi Zanjabil
  76,18,Kasupe amene ali komweko wotchedwa Salsabil